            <h2 class="text-sm sm:text-lg md:text-2xl xl:text-5xl leading-[35px] lg:leading-[48px] xl:leading-[72px] max-w-[1116px] w-[80%] text-[#AFAFAF]">Hey there! This isn’t just a case study; it’s a story of the work, the process, and the thoughts behind it. My goal is to keep things fun and straightforward, enjoy!</h2>
			<!-- <div class="h-[100px] aspect-[2/4] bg-center bg-contain bg-no-repeat bg-[url('/icons/down_arrow.svg')] absolute left-20 bottom-15"></div> -->
